metadata.name: I AM!
metadata.description:
This piece represents us all: the ones who make something out of nothing (artists), the ones who constantly build, the ones who kept pushing through the hard times, and the ones who gently supported our journey and lifted us (collectors).

A piece for the resilient ones who never gave up, who continuously grow, and do so with unlimited potential and kindness.

This one is for ALL OF YOU.

I AM the creator.  
I AM the entire Universe.  
I AM a unique moment in history.

I AM!
